//Granting permissions to the objects

GRANT {PRIVILEGE} ON {OBJECT} <object_name> TO <user_email/team_name>
GRANT USAGE ON {OBJECT} <object_name> TO <user_email/team_name>

{PRIVILEGE} can be select,modify,delete,all privileges
{OBJECT} can be catalog,schema,table,view,database,function,any file

also : DENY/REVOKE {PRIVILEGE} ON {OBJECT} <object_name><user_email>

//To view all permissions assigned to user
SHOW GRANTS ON {object} database.schema.table(assigned to the user)

//To use UI for all above commands
Databricks ----> Data -----> Data Explorer ---------> Grant/Revoke users using buttons
